    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/windsor" style="color:#c4912a;">Windsor</a>, <a href="/suburbs/lutwyche" style="color:#c4912a;">Lutwyche</a>, <a href="/suburbs/gordon-park" style="color:#c4912a;">Gordon Park</a>, <a href="/suburbs/red-hill" style="color:#c4912a;">Red Hill</a>.</p>
